The identity problem (Part 2)

Part 1: see #339
****
Usagi, Ami, Rei, Makoto,...Minako: Five friends. Together they are the legendary Sailor Team. They fight for our world. They fight for justice, love and beauty. Actually..
****
(Me): "Minako, what has happened? 😰 You remember who you are? Can you recognize your friends around you? And don't you know who I am?"
(Minako): "🤔 There was that noise. A flashing light. Then.. silence. 😥 Everything looks familiar, but far away. I know that the girls around me are my friends. We are part of a team. And I can feel you being special to me..😳😳."
(Me): "Minako..🥰 You are special to me too. Ok, you girls: Usagi, Ami, Rei, Makoto - have you anything in your mind. Something that happened before your bad misfortune?😰"
My hope was destroyed. I looked at empty faces. And no answer.
(Me): "Minako 💘. I believe in you. I believe that you would be able to see behind oblivion. Your heart is strong. Use it to remember. Here! I have something for you that would help you to remind."
I took the flyer of the First Aid course, she recently taught and my Valentine -Letter for her out of my trousers pocket.
(Minako): "😮😊🥰 Yes! I feel, that we know each other. Now I remember that I've made this flyer. You you were a bad student, because you wantet me to show you how to become rescued again and again! 😆 And you wrote this for me!😍💘. Oh my beauty goddess."
(Me): "😍 You begin to remember. I think You are steady now without getting a shock. Time for the backup-mirror you gave me for situations like this!"
She looked in that huge mirror I've placed in front of her. For one moment she seemed to faint again, but then..
(Minako): "A_Sailor_Venus_Collection 😊😍💘! It's everything back again. My name, my friends, my world rescueing task.. my love😳💘. And I know how to get back the mind of my friends. Usagi, Ami, Rei, Makoto. I'll heal you as far as I'm the goddess of love!😉"
..(To be continued)..

